# FILE: home/searchArchive/searchResults.desc
# ROLE: Full-Page Search Archive
# ROUTE: /search?q=...
# ACCOUNT: All — results shown regardless of account type
# THEME: Dark · filter sidebar · modular result cards

## 1. HEADER SYNC & MODAL → PAGE TRANSITION
- When "عرض جميع النتائج" is clicked in the header search modal → navigates to /search with query param
- URL STATE: /search?q=react keeps query in sync with input
- IDLE STATE: if no query → placeholder "ابحث في المنصة..."

## 2. LAYOUT
- STICKY SIDEBAR (start side · RTL):
  - CATEGORY CHIPS: [الكل] [📚 المكتبة] [🎓 الأكاديمية] [💼 المستقلون] [🛒 المتجر]
  - FILTERS: Date Range · Access (مجاني/مدفوع) · Faculty Tags
- MAIN PANEL:
  - HEADER: "النتائج لـ 'React'" + "142 نتيجة" — text-[#4A5D78] monospace
  - GRID: modular cards (LibraryCard, CourseCard, FreelancerCard, ProductCard)
    - Each card matches the style of its parent section

## 3. FILTER CHIPS (Quick-Filter)
- HORIZONTAL ROW at top of results panel
- Tags: 🛠️ هندسة · ⚖️ قانون · 💻 تقنية · 🏥 طب ...
- Click → instant re-filter without page reload

## 4. EMPTY STATE
- ILLUSTRATION: simple dark illustration or icon
- TEXT: "لا توجد نتائج مطابقة — جرّب كلمات أخرى"
- SUGGESTION: 3 popular search tags to try

## 5. ACCOUNT TYPE IMPACT
- Guest: sees all results but "تسجيل الدخول لتحميل / للتسجيل" gates on certain actions
- Student: can download library docs, enroll in courses directly from results
- Business: can view + purchase store items · freelancers can appear in talent results
- Admin: sees extra edit icon on each result card
